  "body": "## Simple Summary\r\n\r\n## Abstract\r\n\r\n## Motivation\r\n`throw` is undocumented, and `raise` is already python syntax. Also, reason strings are now available for revert.\r\n\r\n## Specification\r\nRemove the `throw` function, and add `raise` to the grammar which requires a reason string. The behavior of `raise <reason_string>` should be the same as `assert False, <reason_string>`.\r\n\r\n## Backwards Compatibility\r\nRemoves `throw` but it's undocumented.\r\n\r\n## Dependencies\r\nNone but related to https://github.com/ethereum/vyper/pull/1325\r\n\r\n## Copyright\r\nCopyright and related rights waived via [CC0](https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/)\r\n",
